### Phase 15j: URL Redirect System (FUTURE - 6+ months)
**Goal**: Prevent broken links when topic slugs are changed by implementing automatic redirects.

- [ ] **Slug History Tracking** - Store previous slugs when topics are renamed in a `topic_slug_history` collection
- [ ] **Automatic Redirects** - Implement 301 redirects from old slugs to new slugs in Next.js middleware
- [ ] **Redirect Management UI** - Admin interface to view and manage redirects (view history, manually add redirects)
- [ ] **Redirect API** - Backend endpoint to handle slug lookups and redirect resolution
- [ ] **Analytics Integration** - Track redirect usage to identify frequently accessed old URLs
- [ ] **Bulk Redirect Import** - Support importing redirect rules from CSV for migrations
- [ ] **Redirect Expiry** - Optional TTL for redirects (e.g., expire after 1 year if never used)

