### Phase 16c: Progressive Disclosure & Mental Models (MEDIUM-TERM - 4-8 weeks)

**Principle**: "Show summary first, reveal depth on demand. Frame the app as infinite thinking space."

#### 8. Progressive Disclosure System
- [ ] **Level 1: Glance** - Title + 1-sentence definition visible without interaction
- [ ] **Level 2: Summary** - 2-3 key points, primary sources, related topics (expandable)
- [ ] **Level 3: Article** - Full article content with sections
- [ ] **Level 4: Deep Dive** - All sources, scholarly notes, alternative interpretations
- **Implementation**: Redesign `TopicExperience.tsx` with collapsible depth levels
- **Done When**: User can get value in 5 seconds OR spend 30 minutes‚Äîtheir choice

#### 9. "Infinite Space" Graph Exploration
- [ ] **Zoom-based navigation** - Zoom out = see more connections, zoom in = see detail
- [ ] **No dead ends** - Every topic connects to at least 2 others
- [ ] **Breadcrumb trail** - Show how user navigated to current concept
- [ ] **"Explore from here"** - Always visible prompt to continue exploring
- **Implementation**: Enhance graph component with zoom levels, add exploration prompts
- **Done When**: User feels they could explore forever; no "I've seen everything" feeling

#### 10. Nested Content Views
- [ ] **Articles embed mini-topics** - Inline expandable topic definitions within articles
- [ ] **Topics embed source snippets** - Show key quotes directly in topic view
- [ ] **Sources link back to topics** - Every source shows which topics reference it
- [ ] **Recursive exploration** - Can go from topic ‚Üí source ‚Üí different topic ‚Üí source
- **Implementation**: Create `EmbeddedTopic`, `SourceSnippet` components with lazy loading
- **Done When**: User can explore deeply without losing context of where they started

---

### Phase 16d: Embed Everything Philosophy (MEDIUM-TERM - 6-10 weeks)

**Principle**: "Support embedding diverse content types for rich learning experiences."

#### 11. Multi-Content Embedding
- [ ] **Sefaria text embedding** - Inline Torah texts via Sefaria API
- [ ] **Audio shiurim embedding** - Embedded audio players for related lectures
- [ ] **PDF manuscript viewing** - In-app PDF viewer for original sources
- [ ] **YouTube/video embedding** - Video lectures related to topics
- [ ] **External source previews** - Rich previews for HebrewBooks, Otzar HaChochma links
- **Implementation**: Create `EmbedContainer` component with content-type detection
- **Done When**: User doesn't need to leave app for supplementary content

#### 12. "Spark Ideas" Serendipitous Discovery
- [ ] **"Unexpected Connection" feature** - Surface surprising topic relationships
- [ ] **Random related quote** - Show quote from different era/source on same concept
- [ ] **"Did you know?"** - Contextual facts that appear based on what user is reading
- [ ] **Cross-reference alerts** - Notify when reading something that connects to previous reading
- **Implementation**: Create `SerendipityEngine` service, integrate into topic views
- **Done When**: Users regularly discover connections they didn't know existed

