## üß† AI-GENERATED SUGGESTIONS (Based on User Priorities)

### Suggested Features & Improvements (For User Review)

#### 16. Progressive Onboarding Flow
- **Idea**: Guide new users through key features on first visit
- **Implementation**: Show tooltips/modals for: search, topics, graph, collections
- **Benefit**: Reduces learning curve; increases feature discovery
- **Effort**: 2-3 days
- **Priority**: Medium

#### 17. Smart Topic Recommendations
- **Idea**: Show "You might also like" based on viewing history
- **Implementation**: Track viewed topics; recommend related topics
- **Benefit**: Increases engagement; helps discovery
- **Effort**: 3-4 days
- **Priority**: Medium

#### 18. Offline Support
- **Idea**: Cache viewed topics for offline access
- **Implementation**: Service worker + IndexedDB for offline storage
- **Benefit**: App works without internet; better mobile experience
- **Effort**: 4-5 days
- **Priority**: Low

#### 19. Dark/Light Mode Toggle
- **Idea**: Let users choose their preferred theme
- **Implementation**: Add theme toggle; persist preference
- **Benefit**: Better accessibility; personal preference
- **Effort**: 1-2 days
- **Priority**: Low

#### 20. Topic Comparison View
- **Idea**: Compare 2-3 topics side-by-side
- **Implementation**: Add "Compare" button; show topics in columns
- **Benefit**: Easier to understand relationships; better learning
- **Effort**: 2-3 days
- **Priority**: Medium

#### 21. Advanced Search Filters
- **Idea**: Filter topics by: category, date added, content completeness, etc.
- **Implementation**: Add filter UI; wire to search API
- **Benefit**: More powerful discovery; better search experience
- **Effort**: 2-3 days
- **Priority**: Medium

#### 22. Topic Timeline View
- **Idea**: Show topics organized by historical period
- **Implementation**: Add timeline visualization; filter by era
- **Benefit**: Historical context; different exploration mode
- **Effort**: 3-4 days
- **Priority**: Low

#### 23. Collaborative Annotations
- **Idea**: Allow users to add notes/highlights to topics
- **Implementation**: Create annotations collection; show on topic page
- **Benefit**: Community knowledge sharing; deeper engagement
- **Effort**: 4-5 days
- **Priority**: Medium

#### 24. Export/Print Functionality
- **Idea**: Export topics as PDF or markdown
- **Implementation**: Add export button; generate document
- **Benefit**: Offline study; sharing; archiving
- **Effort**: 2-3 days
- **Priority**: Low

#### 25. Topic Versioning & History
- **Idea**: Show edit history for topics; ability to revert
- **Implementation**: Track changes in database; show history UI
- **Benefit**: Transparency; error recovery; audit trail
- **Effort**: 3-4 days
- **Priority**: Medium

